channel.title: Hello all :D
channel.description: Hello everyone. I was looking for a community on google and stumbled upon Mopar Game Development. I was looking through some posts a little and decided that this looked like a decent community, a little dead to be honest, but something drew me here. I am a recent college grad and and me and some buddies decided to start a sort of indie team called n-Development using our own engine called "n-gen". We just created a website (not more than a few hours ago), but I won't advertise it out of respect for this forum. If you would like to see it just PM me and I will send the link. Anyways, we are thinking up ideas right now for our first official game as a team and hope to see what this community thinks about it :D. I hope to get to know some of you better and can't wait to see some of your work.
